  </span></span></span><![endif]><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
  "MS Mincho";mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>увеличение или сохранение могущества; <o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=Normal style='margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6;
  tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
